{
  "info": {
    "name": "Hobit — Live Tracking (Firebase RTDB)",
    "description": "Live tracking API (On My Way mode).\n\nFlow:\n1. Worker app -> POST /tracking/start  (returns firebase_custom_token + driver_path)\n2. Worker app writes GPS straight to Firebase RTDB at driver_path (NOT tested here)\n3. Customer app -> GET /tracking/{booking_id}  (returns read token + worker + destination)\n4. Customer app listens to Firebase RTDB (NOT tested here)\n5. Worker app -> POST /booking/end-service (existing; auto-stops tracking)\n   or POST /tracking/stop (optional)\n\nSet the collection variables first:\n- base_url        : e.g. https://hobitadmin.hobit.club/api  (or http://localhost/Hobit/public/api for local)\n- worker_token    : Sanctum bearer token of a logged-in WORKER\n- customer_token  : Sanctum bearer token of the booking's CUSTOMER\n- booking_id      : a real booking id assigned to that worker",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Worker — Start (On My Way)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json",
            "disabled": false,
            "type": "default"
          },
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json",
            "disabled": false,
            "type": "default"
          },
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{worker_token}}",
            "disabled": false,
            "type": "default"
          }
        ],
        "auth": {
          "type": "noauth"
        },
        "description": "Worker taps 'On My Way'. Creates a tracking session and returns:\n- firebase_custom_token  -> worker app signs in (signInWithCustomToken) on hobitpartner\n- driver_path            -> where the worker app writes GPS (e.g. drivers/12)\nAlso sends the customer a 'worker on the way' FCM push.",
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/tracking/start",
          "protocol": "",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "tracking",
            "start"
          ],
          "query": [],
          "variable": []
        },
